			<p class="m-0 text-ink text-2xl font-semibold leading-tight">ML Engineer with 7+ years of industry experience, pivoting to AI Safety research to work on one of the most important problems of our time.</p>

			<p class="m-0 text-muted">I assign high probability to transformative AI arriving soon. I'm sure it will be wild — and there are real alignment and societal risks on the horizon. I focus on making contributions that optimize for worlds where humans flourish in the long run and the transformation happens cleanly.</p>

